720259f-a.title: Manhattan: Greenwich Street - Bank Street
720259f-a.text:
767-761 Greenwich Street, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner of
Bank Street, as seen through clearance on the S.W. corner. No. 767 is a
1-story frame structure. Elevated shown, is the Ninth Ave. Line.
July 17, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
